feedback: I love this app! It's so easy to use and saves me a lot of time.
The app crashes every time I try to upload a file. Very frustrating!
Would be great if you could add a dark mode feature. My eyes hurt at night.
The interface is confusing. It took me forever to find the settings.
Amazing product! Customer support is also very responsive and helpful.
App is too slow when loading large datasets. Need better performance.
I wish there was an option to export data to Excel format.
Bug in the search function - it doesn't return accurate results.
Great app but needs better integration with Google Calendar.
The mobile version is terrible. Buttons are too small and hard to click.
Love the new dashboard update! Much cleaner and more intuitive.
Please add multi-language support. We need Spanish and French options.
Notification system is broken. I never receive important alerts.
The app is good but could use better security features like 2FA.
Excellent tool for project management. Saves our team hours each week.
I suggest adding a feature to schedule automatic backups.
The app freezes when I try to access the reports section.
Would like to see better collaboration tools for team projects.
Login process is too complicated. Should support single sign-on.
Outstanding app! The analytics dashboard provides great insights.
